CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Flash Newspicture Magazine, January 17, 1938, pg. unknown, reads: "'The Chief' of the Pgh. Courier, Ira F. Lewis and Mrs. Harriet Lewis partaking of a bit of champagne at the Loendi Club bar just prior to the dance of the fashionable Matron's and Maid's in Pgh. during the holidays. (Photos by Cameraman Chas. 'Teenie' Harris)."
TitMainTitle: Ira F. Lewis pouring champagne for Harriet Lewis, in bar of Loendi Club with Christmas decorations
